- When explaining logic, behavior, trade-offs, or workflows, prefer concrete examples and realistic scenarios over abstract description.
- For agent-browser, call isolated state `ctx` or `context`, not `profile`.
- User may mix English with romanized Thai (for example, `na` or `mai`). Reply in English unless asked otherwise.
